---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Kicker from "../components/Kicker.astro";
import Pullquote from "../components/Pullquote.astro";

// Sticky 目录
const sections = [
  { id: "who",     label: "Ⅰ · Who I am",          label_zh: "我是谁" },
  { id: "doing",   label: "Ⅱ · What I'm doing",    label_zh: "我在做什么" },
  { id: "think",   label: "Ⅲ · How I think",        label_zh: "我怎么想的" },
  { id: "site",    label: "Ⅳ · This site",          label_zh: "这个站" },
];
---

<Base
  title="About — conilab"
  description="Articles published twice — once in 中文, once in English. ≥ 3000 字 per piece. About the project, the name, and the writer."
>
  <section class="about">
    <div class="wrap about-grid">
      <!-- ── ASIDE: sticky TOC ── -->
      <aside class="about-aside" aria-label="Section index">
        <div class="aside-inner">
          <Kicker text="contents · 目录" />
          <ol class="toc">
            {sections.map((s) => (
              <li>
                <a href={`#${s.id}`}>
                  <span class="toc-en">{s.label}</span>
                  <span class="toc-zh cjk" lang="zh">{s.label_zh}</span>
                </a>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ol>
          <div class="aside-foot">
            <p class="aside-handle">
              <span class="cjk" lang="zh">@coni</span> ·
              <a href="https://github.com/coni555" rel="me">github</a> ·
              <a href="/articles/rss.xml">rss</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <!-- ── MAIN: bilingual longform ── -->
      <article class="about-main">
        <header class="about-head">
          <Kicker text="about · 关于" />
          <h1 class="about-title">
            @coni
          </h1>
          <p class="about-lede cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            对你自己负责，对你的<em>产品</em>负责。
          </p>
          <p class="about-lede-en" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            Own yourself. Be responsible for your <em>product</em>.
          </p>
        </header>

        <!-- Ⅰ -->
        <section id="who" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅰ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">我是谁</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">Who I am</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              <strong>@coni</strong>，来自 <em>coin</em>——硬币翻个面，<code>c-o-i-n</code> 变成 <code>c-o-n-i</code>。
            </p>
            <p>
              硬币有两面，人也一样。一面<em>向内</em>：记录、阅读、写作、自我修正。一面<em>向外</em>：写代码、造工具、探索 AI、把想法变成能跑的东西。
            </p>
            <p>
              不急着给自己贴标签。先做，做完再看自己变成了什么。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              <strong>@coni</strong> — from <em>coin</em>, flipped: <code>c-o-i-n</code> becomes <code>c-o-n-i</code>.
            </p>
            <p>
              A coin has two faces, and so does a person. One turned <em>inward</em>: journaling, reading, writing, self-correction. One turned <em>outward</em>: coding, building tools, exploring AI, turning thoughts into things that run.
            </p>
            <p>
              No rush to label myself. Do the work first — see what shape I become.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅱ -->
        <section id="doing" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅱ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">我在做什么</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">What I'm doing</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              运营——用户增长侧<em>实习</em>中。同时保持几条自己的线：
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Vibe coding：用 AI 把想法快速变成可用的产品</li>
              <li>持续记录<em>超 365 天</em>，一天不断</li>
              <li>练习写作，长文和小说都在写</li>
              <li>定投 ing——相信时间比择时重要</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              Working in ops — <em>user growth</em> side, as an intern. Meanwhile keeping a few lines of my own:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Vibe coding — turning ideas into working products with AI</li>
              <li>Journaling for <em>365+ days</em> straight, no breaks</li>
              <li>Practicing writing — long-form essays and fiction</li>
              <li>DCA investing — trusting time over timing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Ⅲ -->
        <section id="think" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅲ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">我怎么想的</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">How I think</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              核心信念只有一条：<strong>行动 &gt; 认知</strong>。
            </p>
            <p>
              道理看再多，没有变成行动就是零。我不缺"知道"，缺的是"做到"——所以这个站存在的意义，
              不是展示我懂什么，而是逼自己把想法<em>写完整</em>。写完整本身就是一种行动。
            </p>
            <p>最近很喜欢的一句话——</p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              One core belief: <strong>action &gt; cognition</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
              No amount of knowing matters if it doesn't become doing. I don't lack insight — I lack <em>consistency</em>. So this site exists not to showcase what I understand, but to force myself to write a thought <em>all the way through</em>. Finishing is itself an act.
            </p>
            <p>A line I keep coming back to lately —</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <Pullquote
          zh="你可以外包你的思考，但你不能外包你的理解。"
          en="You can outsource your thinking, but you cannot outsource your understanding."
          side="back"
        />

        <!-- Ⅳ -->
        <section id="site" class="about-sec">
          <h2 class="sec-num">Ⅳ</h2>
          <h3 class="sec-h">
            <span class="cjk" lang="zh">这个站</span>
            <span class="sec-h-en">This site</span>
          </h3>

          <div class="prose cjk" data-lang="zh" lang="zh">
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> = coni + lab。一份个人实验簿。
            </p>
            <p>
              没有日更，没有热点，没有评论区。要回应这里的某个想法，去你自己的笔记本里写一遍。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="prose" data-lang="en" lang="en">
            <p>
              <strong>conilab</strong> = coni + lab. A personal experiment book.
            </p>
            <p>
              No daily posts, no trend-chasing, no comments. The way to respond to a thought here is to go write your own.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about { padding: var(--sp-44) 0 var(--sp-96); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-72);
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--sp-32);
    }
  }

  /* ─── ASIDE ─── */
  .about-aside {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--sp-72) + var(--sp-22));
    align-self: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-aside { position: static; }
  }
  .aside-inner {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--accent-front);
    padding-top: var(--sp-18);
  }
  .toc {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: var(--sp-18) 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-12);
  }
  .toc a {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--sp-2);
    padding: var(--sp-4) 0;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    transition: color var(--dur-quick);
  }
  .toc a:hover { color: var(--accent-front-ink); }
  .toc-en {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-front);
  }
  .toc-zh {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-md);
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }

  .aside-foot {
    margin-top: var(--sp-32);
    padding-top: var(--sp-18);
    border-top: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
  }
  .aside-handle {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .aside-handle a { color: var(--ink-2); }
  .aside-handle a:hover { color: var(--accent-front-ink); }

  /* ─── MAIN ─── */
  .about-main {
    max-width: 64ch;
  }

  .about-head {
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-32);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-44);
  }
  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-7xl), 4.4vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    margin: var(--sp-12) 0 var(--sp-22);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .about-title :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
  }
  .about-lede {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    line-height: var(--lh-prose);
    color: var(--ink-2);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-12);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }
  .about-lede :global(em) {
    font-style: normal;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: var(--cjk-em-line);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-front);
    text-decoration-thickness: var(--cjk-em-thickness);
    text-underline-offset: var(--cjk-em-offset);
  }
  .about-lede-en {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
    color: var(--ink-3);
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }

  /* ─── SECTION ─── */
  .about-sec {
    margin: var(--sp-44) 0;
    scroll-margin-top: var(--sp-96);
  }
  .sec-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-7xl);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--accent-front);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-4);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .sec-h {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    margin: 0 0 var(--sp-22);
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: var(--sp-10);
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--sp-12);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .sec-h .cjk {
    font-family: var(--cjk-serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-3xl);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .sec-h-en {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
  }

  /* ─── PROSE ─── */
  .prose {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    line-height: var(--lh-prose);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .prose.cjk { font-family: var(--cjk-serif); }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 var(--sp-14); }
  .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .prose strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: var(--fw-medium); }
  .prose em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent-back-ink);
    font-weight: var(--fw-light);
  }
  .prose.cjk em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-style: var(--cjk-em-line);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-front);
    text-decoration-thickness: var(--cjk-em-thickness);
    text-underline-offset: var(--cjk-em-offset);
  }
  .prose a {
    color: var(--accent-front-ink);
    border-bottom: var(--sp-hairline) solid var(--accent-front);
  }
  .prose code {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.92em;
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--ink) 5%, var(--paper));
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  /* —— prose 段落上下间距：相邻 zh/en 段在 show-both 模式下用一道 hairline 分隔 —— */
  .prose + .prose {
    margin-top: var(--sp-14);
    padding-top: var(--sp-14);
    border-top: var(--sp-hairline) dashed var(--rule);
  }
  :global(html.show-zh) .prose + .prose,
  :global(html.show-en) .prose + .prose {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  /* ─── PROSE LIST ─── */
  .prose ul {
    padding-left: var(--sp-22);
    margin: var(--sp-8) 0 var(--sp-14);
  }
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);
  }
</style>
